  "title": "Account Management Executive (Sales Support) #81474",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Freight Forwarder</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Account Management Executive (Sales Support)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Central – Marymount</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days / Mon-Fri: 8.45am - 6pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD 4000 + AWS + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Handle sales enquiries, prepare, and present quotations</li><li>Communicate clearly and effectively with both internal teams and external stakeholders</li><li>Develop and implement sales strategies and marketing plans</li><li>Deliver excellent customer service to ensure customer satisfaction and build long-term customer relationships</li><li>Follow up on cold calls and potential leads to drive sales and achieve targets</li><li>Prepare and submit month-end sales reports</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. O level</li><li>Min. 1 year of related experience in freight forwarding or logistics industry</li><li>Experience in account management / Sales within the freight forwarding or logistics industry is preferred</li><li>Primarily responsible for managing and growing existing customer accounts (farmer role)</li><li>Possess class 3 license is a plus</li><li>Company car will be provided for client visits when required (not on a frequent basis)</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81474 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
